OL,3,CAnger over plans to axe some bus
OL,4,Cservices
OL,6,FThere's anger at plans to axe some bus
OL,7,Fservices in Hampshire from the end of
OL,8,Fthe month.
OL,10,FCampaigners say it will leave some
OL,11,Fvillages without a service for the
OL,12,Ffirst time in a generation.
OL,14,FBus users have told ITV Meridian they
OL,15,Fwill be left stranded and are not sure
OL,16,Fhow some children will get to school.
OL,18,FThey also say consultation over the
OL,19,Fcuts has been poor and many were
OL,20,Funaware of the changes until now.
