OL,6,FHowever some routes will see services
OL,7,Fimprove including:
OL,9,FA spokesperson for Hampshire County
OL,10,FCouncil said: "Like many local
OL,11,Fauthorities across the country,
OL,12,FHampshire County Council continues to
OL,13,Fface significant and well-documented
OL,14,Ffinancial pressures.
OL,16,F"In autumn 2024, the Council reviewed
OL,17,Fsavings proposals across 13 service
OL,18,Fareas, including passenger transport
OL,19,Fas part of efforts to balance the 2025/
OL,20,F26 budget.
